<div class="title">Two OTTO interfaces</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The market OTTO offers two interfaces: <strong>Cooperation</strong> and <strong>Integration</strong>. Both interfaces are supported by plentymarkets.<br>
There is a difference in the order import for the two interfaces. When using the <strong>Cooperation</strong> interface, OTTO will transfer individual orders to your plentymarkets system which you can process and ship directly to your end customer.<br>
With the <strong>Integration</strong> interface, your plentymarkets system exchanges one multi-order per day with OTTO. In this case, OTTO ships the ordered items to the end customer.</p>
